    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it's just... people always say \"it gets better\" or \"hang in there,\" but they don't really get it. it feels like everyone is just trying to force me to keep suffering. if there's truly no light at the end, why is it considered \"bad\" to just accept the end?",
